##Steps used for building th eiso image:

1. Create a yaml file -  config.yaml
2. Create an ignition file using coreos-installer binary.
--https://www.vultr.com/docs/ignition
3. Use binary **coreos-installer** to produce ISO image.
--https://coreos.github.io/coreos-installer/iso-embed-ignition/
4. Use rpm-ostree to install all packages.
5. Test it on pendrive. 
